  "text": "Secondary analyses examined the effects of the interventions on individual cognitive tests. Based on prior studies, [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] we hypothesized a priori that the effects of EX-I would be greatest for measures of executive function, especially the EFT incongruent task, and that the effects of the MA-I would be greatest for the UFOV test, which is similar to one of the games in the training program.",
